UID:80d29eb5-9596-4d3e-a192-ca4e77b68f44
DTSTART:20260803T120000
DTEND:20260809T210000
DESCRIPTION:Build a Modern Windsor Rocking Chair with Chairmaker Luke A. Ba
 rnett. Students will join us for a 7-day class. We will start with logs on
  Monday morning and finish with a rocking chair on Sunday. With a maximum 
 of 5 students\, you'll receive personalized instruction in a fully equippe
 d woodworking college with state-of-the-art work benches.
SUMMARY:Modern Windsor Rocking Chair
URL;VALUE=URI:https://ce.sbwi.edu/s/courseoffering/0P0Hu000000TbwNKAS
END:VEVENT
